author: Kevin Goddard
title: Lil Durk - Internet Feat. Young Thug
text:
3 NOT FEELING IT 7 MAKE IT STOP Lil Durk & Young Thug team up for the new banger "Internet," off DJ Bandz's "Chilanta 3" tape. 
Chicago’s DJ Bandz just released a new mixtape today called Chilanta 3, which as the title depicts features exclusive records from several ATL & Chi-town rappers. One of the most popular records off the tape is this never-before-heard collab between Lil Durk & Young Thug called “Internet,” which is making its rounds this evening. 
Going in over production from Inomek In Da Kitchen, Durk & Thugger rap about the haters talkin' silly on social media & the "internet" in this follow up to Durk's " Watch Out" remix . Hit play and let us know what you think. 
Quotable Lyrics: 
Street nigga getting’ rap chat Ask about me boy Im bout that You just do it for the internet 
- Durk
